  Contributor: Chef Keith W. Cochran Yield: 1 1/2 gallons
  
  Posted to MM-Recipes Digest  by kwcochran@juno.com (Keith W Cochran) on Apr
  7, 1998
 
</step></directions></recipe></recipeml>
